race.comment: The $1 million Subzero. MISS JOELENE (1) made up a stack of ground late to take out The Wave last time out and winning rider Graham sticks in the saddle. Has placed two of three over this staying test and it's hard to knock mares in form. Rates the testing material against this line-up. ENCODER (3) finished runner-up behind MISS JOELENE in The Wave and will be ready to peak now third-up from the spell. Has only missed a quinella spot once in five spins around this circuit and should be right there at the business end. WYMARK (7) is a bit of a hit or miss type but is more than capable enough on his day. Can feature on best figures. SLY BOOTS (11) should be able to sit up on speed and will give backers a sight for a long way. MAJOR BEEL (2) next best from the inside marble.
